title: RIP MY SHRED STICK: PENSACOLA
description: Hurley's Rip My Shred Stick Tour stopped by Pensacola, Florida for another day of fun with some stoked out groms. Waves were fun, thunderstorms were dodged and a winner was crowned. For the full report and photos head over to hurley.com/rmss
